## Steps to Reproduce

1. Execute `flutter run` on the code sample
2. Click on text field
3. Click on FAB multiple times

**Expected results:** <!-- what did you want to see? -->
1. Caret is focused just like when editing using keyboard.

**Actual results:** <!-- what did you see? -->
1. Caret is already at the end of the text (need to scroll all the way), but not focused.

<details>
