2. Open your Flutter app (at Flutter version `3.10.5` or `3.10.6`).
3. Enter the `shortcut` set up and then press the space button in the keyboard, the content will immediately change according to the corresponding `phrase`.
However, if you fill in the `shortcut content` and then wait for about `3 seconds` and then press the `space` button, the `shortcut content` will not change according to the corresponding `phrase`.

Note: 
- If the error has appeared, the next time you do it again, don't wait 3 seconds, it will still fail.
- I have tested on 2 versions of Flutter version `3.10.5` and `3.0.6`. However, when I reverted to version `3.7.10`, this function worked properly.

